column2: Sea Creature freedom fighters operating in this province with the support of the local population, killing our warriors and carrying out robbery raids.
In the course of recent events, local freedom fighters were weakened, but not completely destroyed.
In the course of recent events, local freedom fighters were almost destroyed.
Agitators of sea Creature partisans seriously spurred the aggressiveness of local population, increasing the chance of an uprising.
A rare merchant can travel through this province without losing either his purse or life. Better not to talk about tax collectors.
The constant ambushes and attacks by local partisans groups requires constant presence of troops in this province and make the passage of large armies through this lands extremly difficult.
The Sea Creature Invasion will occur at a random date, though at the earliest 50 years after the game is started.
The Sea Creature Invasion will occur at a random date, though at the earliest 100 years after the game is started.
The Sea Creature Invasion will not occur.
The Sea Creature Invasion will occur right after the game start
